  "title": "Marine Drafter",
  "description": "<p>Key Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Prepare production drawings and deliverables to support project schedule</li><li>Provide design expertise for engineering systems, outfitting and structural design.</li><li>Produce detailed schematic drawings and outfitting construction drawings for the vessel.</li><li>Provide as-built drawings for vessel deliveries.</li><li>Work closely with design project PIC’s on urgent /priority drawings to update.</li></ul><p>Key Skills & Competencies</p><ul><li>Experience in ship’s piping systems, design of mechanical components, and ship’s outfitting design.</li><li>Knowledge of Classification Society regulations and experience in AutoCAD 2D/3D or any CAD software.</li><li>At least Naval Architecture\\ Industrial\\ Mechanical Engineering or any relevant engineering discipline</li><li>At least 2 years of experience</li></ul>",
